Wormsensing develops and commercializes the world’s most sensitive and compact piezoceramic sensors to monitor vibration and deformation in real time. Mapo Tapo is a community-powered platform for booking curated outdoor adventures with certified local guides - from rock climbing in Kalymnos to hiking the Tour du Mont Blanc, backcountry skiing in Norway, and even climbing Nepalese mountains.

The platform combines the reach of a B2C brand with the efficiency of B2B-like distribution, powered by a creative go-to-market engine called The Mesh Engine - a peer-powered alternative to paid advertising.

Traction to date: €1.8M in revenue, 2,200+ travelers from 40+ countries, and a 4.8/5 public rating across 400+ reviews. In 2025, the company is on track to land between €1M and €1.2M in revenue.

Currently raising a €3M Seed+ round to productivize its go-to-market strategy by building scraping algorithms, AI agents, and custom software to automate 99% of operations. €2M already committed by 2 VCs.

KINETK is a first of its kind platform providing anyone with the unprecedented ability to safeguard, track, and control where their content goes, and how it is used. The next generation of IP holders require a robust and transparent system to manage their IP in real-time, across platforms, and without friction. Through the combination of proprietary invisible watermarking, agentic AI detection and tracking, and on-chain registration, KINETK is providing the infrastructure that will underpin the future data models of the digital landscape.
prominent_investors: a16z, Animal Capital, BlackWood Ventures, Blockchain Builders Fund, Tuesday Capital

company_description: HippocrAItes connects multiple patient and health data sources and aggregates all individual's health related data into individual’s own Health Account, creating a largest portfolio on harmonized health data in the industry. We focus on using the data in various use cases to improve personalized healthcare quality and efficiency. Our early used studies suggest that with our Hippo Clinic healthcare system we could initially help save 10 minutes per each patient encounter by presenting the data in a format that helps clinicians to get all relevant health information about their patient at a glance. Next, we will add a marketplace of medical analysis tools, allowing clinicians to connect the data with automated medical analysis, revolutionizing how health data is used.
prominent_investors: TriArch Capital BV

company_description: Our platform enables transparent and reliable voting at any scale and allows users to manage all boards and committees effectively, ulitimately strengthening participation at every level. By combining unprecedented security standards with intuitive usability, we make democratic participation accessible, trustworthy, and future-proof. We use zero-knowledge-proofs, decentralized trust and cutting-edge cryptography to ensure fully verifiable election outcomes. Everything is integrated in one sleek, accessible solution: from elections and board management to meeting organization, document handling, and motion workflows.
